    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3068430/extras/88c898196694fddff8bd5b0256bb39e4.poster.avif?t=1743662104\" width=616 height=180 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3068430/extras/88c898196694fddff8bd5b0256bb39e4.webm?t=1743662104\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3068430/extras/88c898196694fddff8bd5b0256bb39e4.mp4?t=1743662104\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3068430/extras/aa404872ce5662a6fc833ecee720e199.avif?t=1743662104\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3068430/extras_big/aa404872ce5662a6fc833ecee720e199.avif?t=1743662104 width=800 height=104 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3068430/extras/834b126d6b660293863c515e47196557.poster.avif?t=1743662104\" width=620 height=348 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3068430/extras/834b126d6b660293863c515e47196557.webm?t=1743662104\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3068430/extras/834b126d6b660293863c515e47196557.mp4?t=1743662104\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >玩家是1990年代南美洲科尔迪维亚一家私人军事公司的首席执行官。贩毒集团迅速壮大，政府和当地警察迅速腐败。叛军不断寻求发动内战，各国情报机构猖獗。在这个陷入混乱的世界中，雇佣兵公司总是机遇与危机并存。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3068430/extras/0ac0536ba7837af21cdc8537a221f526.avif?t=1743662104\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3068430/extras_big/0ac0536ba7837af21cdc8537a221f526.avif?t=1743662104 width=800 height=104 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3068430/extras/dadb1f7ca2260ea657db40cedf24a2b6.poster.avif?t=1743662104\" width=620 height=348 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3068430/extras/dadb1f7ca2260ea657db40cedf24a2b6.webm?t=1743662104\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3068430/extras/dadb1f7ca2260ea657db40cedf24a2b6.mp4?t=1743662104\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>每一个行动都有其代价。由于政治原因，您的客户不希望透露身份。他们希望其他人来处理肮脏的工作，如果您任务失败，客户不会保护您。然而，您将获得丰厚的报酬作为回报。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3068430/extras/951aa78e64477bb94276bea8c3a02ffd.avif?t=1743662104\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3068430/extras_big/951aa78e64477bb94276bea8c3a02ffd.avif?t=1743662104 width=800 height=104 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3068430/extras/bba6f79a1f134350286d92efbffb463a.poster.avif?t=1743662104\" width=620 height=348 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3068430/extras/bba6f79a1f134350286d92efbffb463a.webm?t=1743662104\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3068430/extras/bba6f79a1f134350286d92efbffb463a.mp4?t=1743662104\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>准备和解决任务的过程包括观察现实的战斗模拟。玩家不直接控制战斗人员，而是作为雇佣兵公司的首席执行官，必须发布更有效的战术指令。第一次尝试任务很难成功。坚持识别敌人的弱点并尝试新战术。雇佣兵小队的成长可能是解决任务的关键。确保在设定的时间内准备好执行任务。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3068430/extras/582f7d038ef1031e38a64aab5937a522.avif?t=1743662104\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3068430/extras_big/582f7d038ef1031e38a64aab5937a522.avif?t=1743662104 width=800 height=104 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3068430/extras/9cf29aa737a109ffb832f8a49b25c8d1.poster.avif?t=1743662104\" width=620 height=348 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3068430/extras/9cf29aa737a109ffb832f8a49b25c8d1.webm?t=1743662104\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3068430/extras/9cf29aa737a109ffb832f8a49b25c8d1.mp4?t=1743662104\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>招募新的雇佣兵，控制他们的武器和战术组合，以及他们在近距离战斗（CQB）情况下的交战规则，以确保任务的成功。作为首席执行官，您将分析雇佣兵小队如何执行任务。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3068430/extras/f9050f950ae3d2464f8e075e6283ba20.avif?t=1743662104\" width=616 height=1362 /></span></p>",
